Freeze hardening: per-game markets exempt + epoch-tagged snapshots

- freezeAtFor(key): futures freeze at ODDS_FREEZE_ISO; per-game knockout markets
  (game:* keys) never freeze here (they open near the knockouts and get their own
  per-match freeze in #20) so the futures freeze does not lock them.
- Snapshots tagged with frozenForIso (the freeze time captured for); a snapshot
  from a different freeze epoch is ignored and re-captured. Robust to date changes
  and self-healing after tests.

Verified on prod: frozen path captures once + serves a stable snapshot (identical
fetchedAt across calls), and reverts cleanly to live.

